    <body>
      <trans-unit id="8580" identifier="4439e81ba1ed2897389a4edfeed27c1d">
        <source>Make a variable called “number of dots” and change its value by setting it
to 1, 2, 4, 8 and 16 respectively.</source>
        <target>crwdns8580:0crwdne8580:0</target>
        <note>Context: XPath: /ul/li</note>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="8581" identifier="54608336d660660ef1ebd256b0f002cf">
        <source>You can find “make a new variable” under the “data” script to create a new
variable.</source>
        <target>crwdns8581:0crwdne8581:0</target>
        <note>Context: XPath: /ul/li</note>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="8582" identifier="57cc55ef262dfe7f5580058f8f4af390">
        <source>Make sure your variable name is meaningful for someone else to read.</source>
        <target>crwdns8582:0crwdne8582:0</target>
        <note>Context: XPath: /ul/li</note>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="8583" identifier="d0b5db533a3d11b4c339c0373ee67a4e">
        <source>In the above example, the variable is called &quot;number of dots&quot; because
it stores the number of dots on a card.</source>
        <target>crwdns8583:0crwdne8583:0</target>
        <note>Context: XPath: /ul/li</note>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="8584" identifier="104bdf64b87fc77d22fd04552d56df79">
        <source>Use the &lt;code&gt;scratch:set [number of dots v] to [0]&lt;/code&gt; block to set the value of
your new variable.</source>
        <target>crwdns8584:0[0]crwdne8584:0</target>
        <note>Context: List Item&#13;
XPath: /ul/li[2]</note>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="8585" identifier="6b0c0c6bcd02cd30ac6237a1abdb49d5">
        <source>Display the value of your variable on the screen by replacing “Hello” in
your &lt;code&gt;scratch:say [Hello] for (2) secs&lt;/code&gt; block with your variable.</source>
        <target>crwdns8585:0[Hello]crwdne8585:0</target>
        <note>Context: List Item&#13;
XPath: /ul/li[3]</note>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="8586" identifier="ddd8e12206694ffb5ab8b1193bdbc3b9">
        <source>The number of seconds tells the output how long to show.
The script waits that long before continuing.</source>
        <target>crwdns8586:0crwdne8586:0</target>
        <note>Context: List Item&#13;
XPath: /ul/li[4]</note>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="8587" identifier="0bfaacae4a79f65af7e6b2743b92fad9">
        <source>Make sure all your blocks are “snapped” together in a line like a jigsaw
puzzle.</source>
        <target>crwdns8587:0crwdne8587:0</target>
        <note>Context: List Item&#13;
XPath: /ul/li[5]</note>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="8588" identifier="ff8db6c3d270691e89444e69b7bdeaed">
        <source>Whenever you click the green flag, your script will start.
To stop, click the stop button.</source>
        <target>crwdns8588:0crwdne8588:0</target>
        <note>Context: List Item&#13;
XPath: /ul/li[6]</note>
      </trans-unit>
